    "slug": "changing-careers-at-thirty-in-india",
    "title": "the switch at thirty",
    "dek": "The switch at thirty is heavier, not braver — how to test it with re-measured aptitude, adjacency maps and runway math instead of romance or panic.",
    "category": "Method",
    "readMin": 4,
    "author": "SetMyCareer Research",
